      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for this. option 1 feels pretty good. i like that it acknowledges their strengths. can you write a second version that's slightly shorter? maybe something a bit more direct but still polite? i dont want it to feel like we're over-explaining things.",
      "source": "evaluator"
